Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:17.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at noon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:20.56,Main,,0,0,0,,you will have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:22.52,Main,,0,0,0,,But you must not meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You must not go to the visitation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:27.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone's here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:32.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Turn around. Go back to your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:35.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:38.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Johngalli A.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:41.33,Main,,0,0,0,,This man was behind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:44.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Johngalli A. is,\Nwithout a doubt, a Stand user.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Just know that you are being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:49.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get you out immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:51.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My handcuffs!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:52.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did I get free?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:55.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, get away from that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:59.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Star Platinum: The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:01.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Time, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:10.44,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:12.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay still! The fight has already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:15.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Aerodynamics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It detected our positions\Nusing aerodynamics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Do not make a move\Nuntil we understand the contraption.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't order me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:30.59,Main,,0,0,0,,-I know that!\N-You… FE40536!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:33.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you're talking to?\NYou bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:35.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:43.93,Main,,0,0,0,,-You…\N-Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:55.11,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll detect our position again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Johngalli A. uses\Nthat Stand to read the airflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:02.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It may even react\Nto the change in our breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:05.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Plus, that Stand can be used remotely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:09.12,Main,,0,0,0,,He can shoot at that Stand\Nto reflect the bullet to his target.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:10.25,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a sniping Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:14.67,Main,,0,0,0,,We cannot attack Johngalli A.,\Nwho is in the men's prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.22,Main,,0,0,0,,We have to destroy that long-range Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:22.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Any damage dealt\Nto the Stand is reflected on its user.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:23.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:27.39,Main,,0,0,0,,The problem is,\Nthe moment we move to prompt an attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:32.02,Main,,0,0,0,,the Stand will detect our position\Nand Johngalli A. will shoot at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay by the wall, Jolyne!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.59,Main,,0,0,0,,It's detecting your location!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:55.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:57.88,Main,,0,0,0,,what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:35.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}EPISODE 4: THE VISITOR (2)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Your own muscles cannot be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.71,Main,,0,0,0,,When skin comes in contact with a breeze,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,the muscles have a twitching reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.47,Main,,0,0,0,,This is an automatic reflex\Nyou cannot control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I use my bones\Nto affix the rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Bones land firmly on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.02,Main,,0,0,0,,The gun is as stable\Nas the surface itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Its stability is something we can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:26.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Meteorologists may argue\Nthat the direction of drafts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.86,Main,,0,0,0,,cannot be predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,That may be true, but only to an extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:36.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this fly flying randomly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:38.12,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:42.84,Main,,0,0,0,,It flies while smelling things nearby\Nand feeling the air current.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.72,Main,,0,0,0,,The wind is the fly's movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Just as the guard said,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Kujo Jotaro is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:03.32,Main,,0,0,0,,He's here to see\Nhis daughter, Kujo Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:07.65,Main,,0,0,0,,The descendant of the Joestars\Nis in the visitation room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.57,Main,,0,0,0,,at this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:13.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Within range of my ability,\NManhattan Transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:16.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Joestar…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.92,Main,,0,0,0,,My life will finally begin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:24.55,Main,,0,0,0,,after I eradicate your family's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:30.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You will pay for robbing me\Nof the one who was my rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:47.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:51.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You said we have to destroy it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:53.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at its movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:56.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It can't detect the wind\Ndue to the precipitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:59.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance! Stone Free!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:01.42,Main,,0,0,0,,No, wait! Look closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's evading every drop of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:10.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's reading the drops' air current\Nto avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, go back to the wall!\NHe's going to shoot at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:22.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't good.{\i}\N{\i1}Once the guards arrive, the air will stir!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.82,Main,,0,0,0,,-Hey, listen!\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:34.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry, move the base of the pillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Kick it with all your might!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,-But you're…\N-Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Got that? Please don't forget what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know why,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:55.22,Main,,0,0,0,,but there's a descending hole\Nbetween the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.22,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems to be a passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:01.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe it leads to\Nthe sewer or the vent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.10,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It may lead us to the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Jolyne.\NSeems it's our only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.07,Main,,0,0,0,,-It flew away…\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.45,Main,,0,0,0,,It's still close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:20.70,Main,,0,0,0,,It's looking for\Nthe perfect angle to snipe us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:21.79,Main,,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:27.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It's following the boy\Non the other side of this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.76,Main,,0,0,0,,He plans to hunt the boy\Nbecause he helped us escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, go down the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I came to break you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Before I entered this room…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:52.78,Main,,0,0,0,,he grabbed this arm of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:54.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it, but he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:01.20,Main,,0,0,0,,He was just an ordinary kid\Nlike you'd see at any park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:04.33,Main,,0,0,0,,And we don't know each other…\NWe're complete strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.12,Main,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he grabbed my arm{\i}\N{\i1}with desperation in his eyes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:14.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The warmth of his hand\Neven felt as if he cared about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:17.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Before he shoots the boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll kill Johngalli A.!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,To the visitation room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.49,Main,,0,0,0,,That's where the fire alarm went off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:39.45,Main,,0,0,0,,There are no cameras there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:41.99,Main,,0,0,0,,-Be prepared to engage!\N-{\i1}Where did he go?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That boy…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:48.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How does he move through this place,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:51.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}appearing and disappearing{\i}\N{\i1}out of nowhere?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:58.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry! To Visitation Room B!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:06.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Did that boy dig this hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,This wall… So he used this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:17.65,Main,,0,0,0,,His height is about 140cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.45,Main,,0,0,0,,His build is small, almost like a child's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:23.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know who he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,but the hole\Nthat suddenly opened is a vent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:28.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I know where it leads by reading the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:29.83,Main,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:35.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't have this small guy\Nguide Jotaro and his daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:38.92,Main,,0,0,0,,deep underground\Nwhere I cannot reach them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:41.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I will not lose those two again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll finish this small one first!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,our situation is too dire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Our Stands are only good\Nfor defense at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:57.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Should we strike, Johngalli A. will read\Nthe movement of the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.24,Main,,0,0,0,,This is too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't just leave the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:04.87,Main,,0,0,0,,This side is the prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,-Good grief.\N-Leave from the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,What the…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.22,Main,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just as I thought, it's chasing the boy!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there aren't any windows here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can he aim through the men's prison?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:41.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No… However…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:45.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This boy… Look at him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:47.62,Main,,0,0,0,,How smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.91,Main,,0,0,0,,No, we're blessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,With his body submerged completely\Nunderwater, the air is unaffected!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:55.00,Main,,0,0,0,,And, he's inside a pipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Johngalli A. cannot find him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Not only that,\Nthere are no windows down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Surely he can't shoot him now…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:08.01,Main,,0,0,0,,The pipe is bursting! But how?\NWhere is he aiming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Could he be…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Distance to the target is 321m.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:31.04,Main,,0,0,0,,The bullet drops 9,5cm while airborne,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:34.37,Main,,0,0,0,,and there's a slight ocean breeze of\N3,2 meters per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:37.04,Main,,0,0,0,,The bullet will drift\Nby 4,2cm to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Finding its target.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:42.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Targeting his heart.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Stone Free!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Threads!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:52.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Kujo Jolyne… This is her Stand ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.60,Main,,0,0,0,,She followed the boy down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:55.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she an imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:58.36,Main,,0,0,0,,She thinks her net can stop my bullet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Changing my target to Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Targeting the forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:05.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I broke this pipe beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:33.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The moment I came in,\NI punctured this gas line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Gas is lighter than air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:40.65,Main,,0,0,0,,It creates a layer of gas\Nseparate from oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:43.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it would obscure your aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Man, was I right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.03,Main,,0,0,0,,How did she do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:50.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You're too late! You're mine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Stone Free!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:01.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Seems you couldn't read your own fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}STAND NAME: MANHATTAN TRANSFER\NSTAND MASTER: JOHNGALLI A.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:13.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:18.98,Main,,0,0,0,,How is a child like you\Nroaming freely about this prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I hit myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:28.49,Main,,0,0,0,,This bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:31.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. You gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:36.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like a bone. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You tried to stop me\Nfrom going to the visitation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Just what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:43.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Not yet… I can't, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You mustn't let that go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,This smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this your doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,That sniper guy, Johngalli A., his Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.73,Main,,0,0,0,,It was nothing once I got to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I pounded it into a thousand pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:10.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems you're quite used to\Nfighting with your Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Not out of choice…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.46,Main,,0,0,0,,There he is! Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:24.46,Main,,0,0,0,,He's on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:29.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Hide! He has a rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:31.34,Main,,0,0,0,,He's hiding behind that pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw him going above the tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:35.05,Main,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:39.43,Main,,0,0,0,,He was targeting from the men's prison,\Nwhich is 200 to 300m away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.98,Main,,0,0,0,,There are layers of bars between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Not only that,\Nhe is almost completely blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:47.15,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you suppose he traveled so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,How the hell should I know?\NIf I said he's here, he's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.41,Main,,0,0,0,,He's directly above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:59.16,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:03.17,Main,,0,0,0,,And get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,The gas must have been accumulating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:16.89,Main,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:19.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:21.48,Main,,0,0,0,,What the…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:23.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did he run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be afraid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Come out and explain what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.90,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:34.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you see where he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.04,Main,,0,0,0,,What boy are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't see him, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:52.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I was talking to a little boy\Noutside the visitation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Johngalli A. tried to\Nget rid of him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Get rid of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:03.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You came here on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:06.31,Main,,0,0,0,,And so I followed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on, our stories aren't matching up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:11.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You must have heard his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:14.19,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I know you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:17.28,Main,,0,0,0,,He's the one who told us\Nabout the secret passage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You were there with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you hear a ghost or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know of a secret passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn you! You're messing with me\Nat a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:30.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You're here now because\Nyou followed me down the secret tunnel…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Something's not right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Your wound…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.52,Main,,0,0,0,,You were shot.\NWhat happened to your wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,The bullet wound\Nfrom when Johngalli A. shot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,On your right shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:51.40,Main,,0,0,0,,But you aren't bleeding, and your clothes…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have a scratch\Nfrom being shot either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:57.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This man…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,He isn't Johngalli A.!\NHe's the prison guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:06.83,Main,,0,0,0,,But I saw him get shot through the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:08.25,Main,,0,0,0,,His head is unscathed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean he was shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.50,Main,,0,0,0,,And who is Johngalli A.?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:18.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something's amiss.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:20.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not adding up!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:28.02,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:38.90,Main,,0,0,0,,A fate more terrible than death\Nwill await us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You must not go to the visitation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The visitation room…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. Something was off{\i}\N{\i1}from the very beginning.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When was I uncuffed?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:53.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that bullet…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was I really shot back there?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:19:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But my dad and I don't have a scratch.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:05.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was Johngalli A.{\i}\N{\i1}attacking us to begin with?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something's wrong.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:09.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing is making sense!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm in a dream of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.07,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I'm under someone's spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.05,Main,,0,0,0,,A dream…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:43.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Was I… dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Since when…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like I did
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.44,Main,,0,0,0,,knock out this prison guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:59.15,Main,,0,0,0,,This photo of Johngalli A…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Dad showed it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:07.95,Main,,0,0,0,,The accident with the hitchhiker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:11.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard that it was all\Na plot to imprison me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.17,Main,,0,0,0,,That was all real.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:18.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then I tried to leave the room.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when I noticed I was uncuffed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the moment.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:29.43,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I was sitting down when I awoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.10,Main,,0,0,0,,So before then…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:35.85,Main,,0,0,0,,We haven't stepped outside\Nof this visitation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:37.90,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:41.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Johngalli A.'s Stand{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:45.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was an illusion my mind created.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The secret passageway too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:56.79,Main,,0,0,0,,The moment we stepped into\Nthis visitation room,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:21:01.67,Main,,0,0,0,,we fell under their trap\Nand were forced to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,As if engulfed by a python,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:07.51,Main,,0,0,0,,slowly but surely,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:09.76,Main,,0,0,0,,we're being melted to the bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:13.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The boy in the garbage can{\i}\N{\i1}who gave me this bone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was real!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was able to wake up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:22.15,Main,,0,0,0,,because I cut myself on this bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:24.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Without the pain from the cut,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I would have stayed asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:33.08,Main,,0,0,0,,This ability is Johngalli A.'s attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:41.21,Main,,0,0,0,,My thread! I can't unravel it,\Nnot even for a few centimeters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:44.46,Main,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:48.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:51.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm getting sleepy again…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:55.81,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:01.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Out of this visitation room!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Stone Free!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Subtitle translation by: Megumi Hunter
